name: Personalized Astrological Chart & Horoscope
description:
Your chart of stars interpreted and explained. We take you on a tour of your stars including pertinent information about your astrological chart and current transits that can effect certain aspects of your life. Astrology is all about timing and timing is everything, as they say. It's not all about crystal-ball tea-leaves bullshit. People were looking up at the stars long before there was Starz on cable.
 
Astrology can help enlighten you because to be aware of the energies at play in your life is to be empowered. "To be or not to be?" That is the Shakespearean question, my dear Watson. Oops, wrong author. "The fault, dear Brutus, is not in the stars but in ourselves." 

Buckle up because this is better than Space Mountain. When you place an order we'll contact you to process and deliver your report. For entertainment purposes, only. We'll enlighten you and you'll be lit up like a roman candle on the Fourth of July. Baby, you're a fiiiirrrreeewoork!
